functions.name: InitializeExternalStartupData
functions.logic: Initializes external startup data by searching for snapshot and natives blob files in the given directory. This function is intended for standalone binaries like d8 or cctest.

functions.name: InitializeExternalStartupDataFromFile
functions.logic: Initializes external startup data using the provided path to the snapshot blob file. This is also meant to be used by standalone binaries.
